snippet.title: The Edge of Reality: Teaser | Doctor Who
snippet.description:
Coming in 2021 to consoles and PC, "Doctor Who: The Edge of Reality" reimagines and builds upon last year’s VR experience, "The Edge of Time" - with a new and compelling first-person adventure! Find out more here: https://bbc.in/3iHo9Yt

WATCH MORE: 
The Edge of Time: http://bit.ly/DW-EdgeOfTime
Thirteenth Doctor: http://bit.ly/TheThirteenthDoctor
Tenth Doctor: http://bit.ly/DWTenthDoctor
Subscribe to Doctor Who for more exclusive videos: http://bit.ly/SubscribeToDoctorWho

MORE ABOUT DOCTOR WHO:
Welcome to the Doctor Who Channel! Travel in the TARDIS with clips dating back to the Doctor's first incarnation in 1963, all the way through dozens of regenerations. Including behind-the-scenes footage, exclusive videos and our very own show Doctor Who: The Fan Show - this is the place to find all the best official clips.
#DoctorWho
